BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//sport.guardian.co.uk/news/story/0%2C10488%2C1414839%2C00.html"&gt;Thorpe to miss Montreal&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGaurdian%20Unlimited%20Sport"&gt;Gaurdian Unlimited Sport&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nzherald.co.nz/index.cfm%3Fc_id%3D4%26amp%3BObjectID%3D10011175"&gt;Thorpe taking year off&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20New%20Zealand%20Hearld"&gt;The New Zealand Hearld&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005

</ul>


