BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//msn.foxsports.com/nhl/story/3400752"&gt;NHL will never be the same&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFox%20Sports"&gt;Fox Sports&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/sports/hockey/articles/2005/02/16/nhl_cancels_season_over_labor_dispute/"&gt;NHL cancels season over labor dispute&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Boston%20Globe"&gt;The Boston Globe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
