BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//npr.streamsage.com/google/programlist/feature.php%3Fwfid%3D%3A//www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php%3FstoryId%3D4500547"&gt;Judge Rules Against Reporters Who Would Not Reveal Sources&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANational%20Public%20Radio"&gt;National Public Radio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 15 Feb 2005 (&lt;a href="http%3A//www.npr.org/dmg/dmg.php%3FprgCode%3DME%26amp%3BshowDate%3D15-Feb-2005%26amp%3BsegNum%3D17%26amp%3BNPRMediaPref%3DRM%26amp%3BgetAd%3D1"&gt;audio&lt;/a&gt;)
BULLET::::- Carol D. Leonnig. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.chicagotribune.com/news/nationworld/chi-0502160262feb16%2C1%2C6644359.story%3Fcoll%3Dchi-newsnationworld-hed%26amp%3Bctrack%3D1%26amp%3Bcset%3Dtrue"&gt;Court: Reporters must reveal sources&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 16, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mcall.com/news/opinion/all-editorial1feb18%2C0%2C3857597.story%3Fcoll%3Dall-newsopinion-hed"&gt;Chilling court decisions should prompt Congress to help reporters protect sources&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMorning%20Call"&gt;Morning Call&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 18, 2005
