BULLET::::- Michael Paulson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/globe/spotlight/abuse/stories3/121402_resignation.htm"&gt;A church seeks healing&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston.com"&gt;Boston.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Decemeber 14, 2002
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/globe/spotlight/abuse/"&gt;The Boston Globe spotlight investigation on abuse in the Catholic church&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston.com"&gt;Boston.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,
BULLET::::- Robert Aicardi. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www2.townonline.com/holbrook/localRegional/view.bg%3Farticleid%3D188031"&gt;Shanley sentenced to 12-15 years in jail&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHolbrook%20Sun"&gt;Holbrook Sun&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 18, 2005

</ul>


