<ul>
BULLET::::- Edward Cody. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A38448-2005Feb19.html"&gt;China Targets Corrupt Officials In a Battle Against Temptation&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 20, 2005
BULLET::::- Geoffrey York. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/ArticleNews/TPStory/LAC/20050215/CHINA15/TPInternational/TopStories"&gt;China wages losing war against gambling&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Globe%20and%20Mail"&gt;The Globe and Mail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 15, 2005
