BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.daily-news.ro/article_detail.php%3Fidarticle%3D6569"&gt;Major part of the privatization program will finish by end of 2006&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABucharest%20Daily%20News"&gt;Bucharest Daily News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 21, 2005
