BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//openfacts.berlios.de/index-en.phtml%3Ftitle%3DWikipedia_Status%26amp%3Boldid%3D8486"&gt;OpenFacts Wikipedia Status&lt;/a&gt;; including text of e-mail sent by Wikimedia developer Brion Vibber
