BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/health/main.jhtml%3Fview%3DDETAILS%26amp%3Bgrid%3DP8%26amp%3BtargetRule%3D10%26amp%3Bxml%3D/health/2005/02/22/hdye22.xml"&gt;Contaminated chilli powder is proving very hard to track down, says David Derbyshire&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Telegraph"&gt;The Telegraph&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 23, 2005

</ul>


