BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.ninemsn.com.au/article.aspx%3Fid%3D37000"&gt;Vatican says Pope back in hospital&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 24 February, 2005
