BULLET::::- Art Harris. "&lt;a href="http%3A//edition.cnn.com/2003/WORLD/asiapcf/central/10/29/afghan.opium/%3FColl%3Dcnn_xml%26amp%3BQuerySubmit%3Dtrue%26amp%3BPage%3D1%26amp%3Bsites%3Dedition%26amp%3BQueryText%3Dart%2Bharris%2Bu.n.%2Bbumper%2Bopium%26amp%3Bquery%3D"&gt;Bumper Afghan opium crop, UN warns&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, October 30, 2003
