BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//edition.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/europe/02/26/amnesty.founder/"&gt;Amnesty International founder dead&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 26, 2005
