</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//dailytelegraph.news.com.au/story.jsp%3Fsectionid%3D1274%26amp%3Bstoryid%3D2732319"&gt;Four die in skyscraper blaze&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Daily%20Telegraph%20%28Australia%29"&gt;The Daily Telegraph (Australia)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 27, 2005

</ul>


