BULLET::::- Lee et. al. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.immunity.com/content/article/abstract%3Fuid%3DPIIS107476130500035X"&gt;VDUP1 Is Required for the Development of Natural Killer Cells&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AImmunity"&gt;Immunity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, February 2005

</ul>
