BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.thestar.com/NASApp/cs/ContentServer%3Fpagename%3Dthestar/Layout/Article_Type1%26amp%3Bc%3DArticle%26amp%3Bcid%3D1109803812095%26amp%3Bcall_pageid%3D970599119419"&gt;Harris plans to deny reports, Allegations about Ipperwash raised&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http%3A//www.thestar.com/"&gt;The Toronto Star&lt;/a&gt;, March 3, 2005.
