BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/4316599.stm"&gt;Fossett sets solo flight record&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC"&gt;BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 3, 2005

