BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.af.mil/news/story.asp%3FstoryID%3D123005322"&gt;AF announces Boeing inquiry results&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAir%20Force%20Print%20News"&gt;Air Force Print News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 25, 2003

