BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/news/world/articles/2005/03/06/report_says_cia_powers_broadened/"&gt;Report says CIA powers broadened Report&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston%20Globe"&gt;Boston Globe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 6, 2005
