BULLET::::- Schweber, S. S. ♡❤In the shadow of the bomb: Bethe, Oppenheimer, and the moral responsibility of the scientist♡❤ (Princeton, N.J.: Princeton University Press), 2000. Quotes about the hydrogen bomb on p. 166.

</ul>
