BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.lifespan.org/news/2005/03/RIH_Alzheimers_3-7-05.htm"&gt;Researchers Discover Link Between Insulin and Alzheimer's&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APress%20release"&gt;Press release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 7, 2005

</ul>


