BULLET::::- Frank Fitzgibbon. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0%2C%2C2095-1512455%2C00.html"&gt;Walsh in the running to replace Eddington at British Airways&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Sunday%20Times"&gt;The Sunday Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 6, 2005
