BULLET::::- Peter Hect. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.miami.com/mld/miamiherald/news/11057579.htm"&gt;Peasants in Peru near showdown on mercury spill&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMiami%20Herald"&gt;Miami Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 5, 2005 ♡❤(free signup)♡❤

