BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.mineralresourcesforum.org/incidents/Cajamarca/"&gt;SAN JUAN, CHOROPAMA AND MAGDALENA, PERU - MERCURY SPILL OF 2 JUNE 2000&lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤Mineral Resources Forum♡❤, 2002

</ul>


