BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//cbs.marketwatch.com/news/story.asp%3Fguid%3D%257BA2D3EC30-B753-446C-83C8-69E872734F86%257D%26amp%3Bsiteid%3Dgoogle%26amp%3Bdist%3Dgoogle"&gt;Taiwanese ADRs slump; China adopts law allowing military attack&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACBS%20MarketWatch"&gt;CBS MarketWatch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 8, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/news/consumer_news/11082149.htm"&gt;U.S. urges China to reconsider Taiwan law&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Kansas%20City%20Star"&gt;The Kansas City Star&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 8, 2005
BULLET::::- Hu Jintao. "&lt;a href="http%3A//en1.chinabroadcast.cn/144/2005-3-7/33%40213791.htm"&gt;Four-point Guideline on Cross-Straits Relations Set Forth by President Hu&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APeople%27s%20Daily"&gt;People's Daily&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 7,2005

