BULLET::::- Stefan Bos. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.voanews.com/english/2005-03-09-voa61.cfm"&gt;Bulgaria Says Soldier Killed by US Troops in Iraq&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AVoice%20of%20America%20News"&gt;Voice of America News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 9, 2005
