BULLET::::- Ken Ramani and Reuters. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.eastandard.net/hm_news/news.php%3Farticleid%3D15097"&gt;Sudan government, donors launch recovery plan&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEast%20African%20Standard"&gt;East African Standard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/IRIN/c60369061224cf1c1056a2df7e8cbb43.htm"&gt;SUDAN: Billions needed for initial recovery and development&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4333575.stm"&gt;Sudan needs billions to rebuild&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 9, 2005

