BULLET::::- Robin Wright. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A29389-2005Mar12.html%3Fsub%3Dnew"&gt;Syria Vows Phased Lebanon Exit&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 13, 2005

</ul>
