</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.xinhuanet.com/english/2005-03/13/content_2690803.htm"&gt;New manhole material introduced to prevent theft&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AXinhua"&gt;Xinhua&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 13, 2005

</ul>


