BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/136613/1/.html"&gt;Taiwan's ruling DPP to rally against China law&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AChannel%20News%20Asia"&gt;Channel News Asia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 14, 2005
BULLET::::- Elaine Kurtenbach. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/news/world/asia/articles/2005/03/04/chinas_military_spending_to_rise/"&gt;China's military spending to rise&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston%20Globe"&gt;Boston Globe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 4, 2005

</ul>


