<doc id="5842" url="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki?curid=5842" title="Brazil defends China against human rights violation charges in UN">
<h1>Brazil defends China against human rights violation charges in UN</h1>
&lt;strong class="published"&gt;&lt;span id="publishDate" class="value-title" title=""&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="Z3988" style="display:none" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rfr_id=rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:User%3ADendodge&amp;rft_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:&amp;rft.atitle=Brazil%20defends%20China%20against%20human%20rights%20violation%20charges%20in%20UN&amp;rft.jtitle=Wikinews&amp;rft.date=&amp;rft.aucorp=Wikinews+contributors&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.rights=CC-BY+2.5&amp;rft.identifier=&amp;rft.artnum="&gt; &lt;/span&gt; 

&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABrazil"&gt;Brazil&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; — Human Rights Secretary Nilmário Miranda said that &lt;a href="w%3ABrazil"&gt;Brazil&lt;/a&gt; will defend &lt;a href="w%3AChina"&gt;China&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href="w%3AUnited%20Nations%20Commission%20on%20Human%20Rights"&gt;United Nations Commission on Human Rights&lt;/a&gt;. According to him, the Chinese showed some advances in the human rights area recently.

Last year Brazil voted for China and helped to stop a discussion on the subject in UN. The only Latin American countries who favored China in 2004 were Brazil and &lt;a href="w%3ACuba"&gt;Cuba&lt;/a&gt;.

<h2>Sources</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//babelfish.altavista.com/babelfish/tr%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A//br.news.yahoo.com/050314/25/siv1.html%26amp%3Blp%3Dpt_en"&gt;Brazil helps China to escape of condemns in the ONU (UN) - Babelfish&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AO%20Estado%20de%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo"&gt;O Estado de São Paulo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 14, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//br.news.yahoo.com/050314/25/siv1.html"&gt;Brasil ajuda China a escapar de condenação na ONU&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AO%20Estado%20de%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo"&gt;O Estado de São Paulo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 14, 2005

</ul>


