BULLET::::- Ben Fenton. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml%3Fxml%3D/news/2005/03/16/nwood16.xml%26amp%3BsSheet%3D/news/2005/03/16/ixhome.html"&gt;Threat to Woodcraft Folk as Hodge wields the axe&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Daily%20Telegraph%20%28UK%29"&gt;The Daily Telegraph (UK)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 16, 2005 (registration required)
