BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.tibet.ca/panchenlama/panchen.html"&gt;Free the Panchen Lama&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Panchen%20Lama%20Website"&gt;The Panchen Lama Website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/2450463.stm"&gt;China says vanished Panchen Lama 'happy'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20Online"&gt;BBC News Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 12 November, 2002
