BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.jamaicaobserver.com/editorial/html/20050317T210000-0500_77071_OBS_MR_WOLFOWITZ_S_NOMINATION.asp"&gt;Mr. Wolfowitz’s Nomination&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Jamaica%20Observer"&gt;The Jamaica Observer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 18, 2005

